                        <interp inst="t18370918-name-925" type="given" value="JOHN"></interp>JOHN WALKER</persName>
                  </hi>. I am a tin-plate-worker, and live at No. 1, Onslow street. The prisoner has been in my service a year and three months—he worked in the trade and went on errands—it was his duty to receive monies on my account.</p>
