                  <hi rend="italic">re-examined</hi>. The prisoner never paid me the 19<hi rend="italic">s</hi>.—if he received it on the 12th, he ought to have paid it on his return, but he did not return at all—I did not see him till he was going to Hatton garden—I had given information to the police, and they took him.</p>
